snippet.title: Campaign Series Vietnam 1948-1967 Full Teaser
snippet.description:
All of the teasers videos that show what to look forward to with the Campaign Series Vietnam 1948-1967 game that will be released on January 20th, 2022. 

You can find more at 
https://cslegion.com/games/vietnam/
and
https://www.matrixgames.com/forums/tt.asp?forumid=1750

Thank you for your interest!

The Devils Pie by Brian Holtz Music
Link: https://filmmusic.io/song/6967-the-devils-pie
License: https://filmmusic.io/standard-license
